## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on what makes a great manager. The findings are limited to the insights provided by the selected sources and may not reflect the latest trends or practices in management. Additionally, the dynamic nature of management practices means that new qualities and skills may emerge over time, which are not covered in this report.